'fullstack ai'.includes('data')      // false
'bonjour monde'.includes('monde')    // true
```

**Application pratique :**
```html
<div data-category="fullstack ai"></div>

<script>
const category = card.getAttribute('data-category'); // "fullstack ai"
category.includes('ai')        // true
category.includes('fullstack') // true
category.includes('data')      // false
</script>
```

---

### style.display
```javascript
